  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put [? on them ?] [? myriad-- ?] [? myriad ?] marks as [INAUDIBLE], as when in [INAUDIBLE], when an attack was made on one of the representatives in the French-- French embassy, which gave them the source for the Kristallnacht and for even more hatred.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember well your question is that this was the hate and propaganda newspaper, paper, issued by Streicher at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember it very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was almost on each corner, like you have here at postal drop box.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So there was a there, and they made it also very cheap to buy, and they made special issues of And what they wrote in the most beautiful language-- it was forbidden for Jews to read, but I nevertheless-- I was a small-- small boy.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I did not know what consequences might have-- from time to time, I took-- I bought one, and I read.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was such hatred, which I still could not grasp that it is going to be to work out something very terrible in the future.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this is how a populace was instigated, instigated to hate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was called And then one other thing which I remember very, very well, when the SR marched through the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In their song, they incorporated a line which was called, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And again, I did not know the horrible implication of this, but this means, and when the blood of the Jews gushes out of the wound, which was inflicted-- which is inflicted from our knives, or from the knives, then we will have it much better.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Unbelievable, and it was in such style.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was sung in a marching-- in the marching band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You see, it was-- and everybody was listening to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
